snippet.title: ★v5.3 [Post-Dusk Odyssey] Trailer★ - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
★v5.3 [Post-Dusk Odyssey] Trailer★ - Honkai Impact 3rd

Honkai Impact 3rd v5.3 [Post-Dusk Odyssey] coming soon! New SP battlesuit [Sweet 'n' Spicy] debuts!
Story Chapter XXVII [Dusk of the Fool] and APHO Chapter 2 Prologue [Before Starfall] are approaching! Stay tuned!
